        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">navigation</ENAMEX>, to aid <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE_DESC">city</ENAMEX> planning. The inventions of the calculus by <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Isaac Newton</ENAMEX> and
        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Gottfried Leibniz</ENAMEX> in the <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">later 17th century</TIMEX> were stimulated by physical problems such as
