        <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">ounces</ENAMEX> in different <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">individuals</ENAMEX>. He estimated that at least <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">one-eighth</NUMEX> and perhaps as much
